apply

public static final <T extends Replaceable<T>> java.util.Set<T> apply(Substitution s,
                                                                      java.util.Set<T> set)
Returns the result of applying the specified substitution to the elements of the specified set.

When the result of applying of the substitution to a given element from the set is invalid, it is not added to the returned set.

Type Parameters:
T - A Replaceable type
Parameters:
s - The substitution to be made
set - The set containing the elements to be substituted
Returns:
The result of applying the specified substitution to the elements of the specified set.
